# <% .Name %>

A workshop built with [worky](https://github.com/davideimola/worky).

## For participants

1. Download the binary from the [releases page](../../releases)
2. Run `./<% .Slug %> serve --open`
3. Follow along in your browser
4. Run `./<% .Slug %> check` to unlock each chapter

## For workshop creators

### Prerequisites

- Go 1.24+
- Hugo (extended)

### Setup

```sh
hugo mod init <% .Module %>
hugo mod get github.com/davideimola/worky
hugo mod get github.com/geekdocs/geekdoc
go mod tidy
```

### Development

```sh
make serve    # build site and run the workshop
make check    # check current chapter progress
make status   # show all chapter statuses
```

### Build and release

```sh
make build    # build for current platform
make release  # cross-compile for all platforms
```

Or push a tag to trigger the GitHub Actions release workflow:

```sh
git tag v1.0.0
git push origin v1.0.0
```
